race.description: Ladbrokes Racing Extras In Multi Handicap
race.comment: VIALE (13) went forward last start over 1000m at Toowoomba and held on well beaten 0.8 lengths. Should enjoy a good run just off the speed and third-up is suitably placed to post another win. BEEN A SECRET (1) used the rails draw to good effect first-up, bouncing straight to the lead and scoring over 1000m at Toowoomba. Was heavily backed and keeps a handy 3kg claim. Draws awkwardly today but has the gate speed to manage. She is sure to take some stopping with the extra fitness. HORRIBLE HANK (2) made it two wins in a row, scoring by 1.5 lengths over 1200m at Chinchilla. Meeting a tougher field, but on current form, he's capable of testing his rivals. TURN UP THE MUSIC (4) fought on last start over 1000m at Toowoomba, beaten 2.2L. Maps well and has decent prospects.
